WEBVTT

01:31.380 --> 01:34.900
=Generation to Generation=

01:35.020 --> 01:37.900
=Episode 29=

01:38.850 --> 01:39.740
Uncle Xue,

01:41.410 --> 01:42.620
what kind of person

01:43.570 --> 01:45.050
was Mu Zhengyang, really?

01:47.290 --> 01:48.130
Zhengyang was...

01:50.210 --> 01:51.050
He...

01:51.660 --> 01:52.850
It's been so many years.

01:53.770 --> 01:55.290
What's there left to hide?

02:02.620 --> 02:03.820
The first time I saw him, he had

02:05.100 --> 02:06.210
(Little Mu Zhengyang)
no family, no home,

02:06.210 --> 02:07.410
just wandering,

02:07.410 --> 02:09.690
fighting dogs for scraps like an animal.

02:10.290 --> 02:12.340
He could barely speak in full sentences.

02:23.340 --> 02:24.340
The village kids

02:25.660 --> 02:26.940
called him a mongrel.

02:27.350 --> 02:28.220
Mongrel!

02:28.220 --> 02:29.780
Nobody wants you!

02:30.100 --> 02:31.060
Little mongrel!

02:31.060 --> 02:32.170
You're not fit to play with us.

02:32.170 --> 02:33.010
Get him!

02:33.290 --> 02:34.540
They were cruel, those kids.,

02:34.540 --> 02:35.540
always picking on him.

02:36.380 --> 02:37.540
But he never broke.

02:37.540 --> 02:38.660
He wouldn't bow to them.

02:39.290 --> 02:40.890
They'd beat him until he bled,

02:41.820 --> 02:42.660
but his eyes

02:43.610 --> 02:45.010
stayed fierce, like a cornered wolf's.

02:48.130 --> 02:50.610
One day, I couldn't just watch.

02:51.940 --> 02:53.100
I stepped in.

02:54.060 --> 02:55.820
- Little mongrel!
Bad guys, bad guys!

02:55.820 --> 02:56.660
- Run! Run!
- Bad guys!

02:58.570 --> 02:59.500
You okay?

03:07.060 --> 03:07.900
Come here.

03:08.980 --> 03:10.500
Good boy. Hang in there.

03:16.940 --> 03:17.780
My mother

03:18.820 --> 03:19.820
saw him, took pity,

03:20.730 --> 03:21.730
took him in.

03:22.690 --> 03:23.690
Careful now.

03:31.100 --> 03:31.940
Easy.

03:35.890 --> 03:36.730
Go on, eat.

03:38.540 --> 03:40.380
But the good times didn't last.

03:42.260 --> 03:43.170
My father

03:44.380 --> 03:45.540
had a hunting accident.

03:46.410 --> 03:49.100
Then the village bullies set their sights
on us.

03:50.170 --> 03:51.340
One night,

03:54.130 --> 03:56.100
they broke in.

04:08.940 --> 04:10.290
Come here. Come on.

04:11.730 --> 04:12.820
Hold still.

04:22.850 --> 04:23.980
You animal!

04:24.780 --> 04:25.620
Let go!

04:26.100 --> 04:26.940
Come on!

04:29.780 --> 04:31.100
No!

04:32.490 --> 04:33.810
Mother!

04:35.410 --> 04:37.290
Mother!

04:37.290 --> 04:40.100
Mother, wake up!

04:40.100 --> 04:41.580
Mother!

04:42.410 --> 04:43.730
Mother!

04:45.020 --> 04:47.700
Please wake up!

04:47.700 --> 04:49.610
Mother!

04:55.340 --> 04:56.660
Mother!

04:58.220 --> 05:00.050
Mother!

05:00.050 --> 05:01.580
Wake up, Mother.

05:04.410 --> 05:06.610
Please wake up.

05:11.290 --> 05:12.610
Mother!

05:14.340 --> 05:15.660
Mother!

05:25.540 --> 05:26.380
Zhengyang.

05:31.900 --> 05:34.170
I have to avenge her.

05:45.930 --> 05:47.340
Some preyed on the helpless

05:48.900 --> 05:50.140
and the others stood there and watched.

05:51.900 --> 05:52.900
Zhengyang said

05:53.930 --> 05:56.100
they all deserve to die for what they did.

06:05.370 --> 06:06.340
What happened then?

06:08.290 --> 06:09.220
After that,

06:12.020 --> 06:13.580
we wandered,

06:14.250 --> 06:15.410
just the two of us.

06:16.370 --> 06:17.490
Until one day, we ran into

06:18.370 --> 06:19.850
someone from the martial world.

06:28.620 --> 06:31.060
(Young Mu Zhengyang)

06:37.020 --> 06:37.860
Water...

06:38.100 --> 06:38.940
Please...

06:39.140 --> 06:40.100
Give me water...

06:45.540 --> 06:46.490
Young Master?

06:47.410 --> 06:48.700
What are you doing here?

06:49.540 --> 06:51.780
You're the heir to the Li Sect.

06:52.340 --> 06:54.660
Get back to the Hanhai Mountains now.

07:03.020 --> 07:03.860
Zhengyang

07:04.370 --> 07:05.610
decided to join the Li Sect.

07:06.850 --> 07:08.220
He had these fragments

07:08.490 --> 07:09.340
from when he was little

07:09.980 --> 07:11.020
and someone feeding him

07:11.580 --> 07:12.540
and holding him.

07:13.700 --> 07:15.610
And there was another child like him.

07:15.610 --> 07:16.490
Maybe that child

07:17.660 --> 07:19.140
was the one they called

07:20.490 --> 07:21.330
Young Master.

07:35.580 --> 07:36.900
Maybe you shouldn't go.

07:37.540 --> 07:39.020
They say those people from the Demon Sect

07:39.020 --> 07:40.290
are savages who would eat you alive.

07:40.610 --> 07:41.450
I have to.

07:42.140 --> 07:43.220
I need to know

07:43.220 --> 07:44.140
who I am.

07:44.810 --> 07:45.650
Youfu,

07:45.980 --> 07:46.820
go back

07:47.730 --> 07:48.570
and wait for me.

07:50.900 --> 07:51.740
Don't worry.

07:52.340 --> 07:53.490
I'll come back alive.

08:16.490 --> 08:17.580
Years later,

08:18.250 --> 08:19.290
he came back.

08:19.850 --> 08:21.340
He was totally different then.

08:24.140 --> 08:24.980
Youfu!

08:26.540 --> 08:27.490
Zhengyang!

08:34.610 --> 08:35.770
Let me look at you!

08:37.890 --> 08:39.100
Sit down,

08:41.340 --> 08:42.180
let me

08:42.180 --> 08:43.130
get you something to eat.

08:48.730 --> 08:49.570
Zhengyang,

08:50.530 --> 08:51.420
what is that

08:51.770 --> 08:52.940
on your back?

08:52.940 --> 08:54.490
What did they do to you?

08:57.250 --> 08:58.090
Youfu,

08:58.610 --> 08:59.450
don't worry.

09:00.010 --> 09:01.420
Everyone who ever hurt me,

09:02.300 --> 09:03.890
I'll make them pay.

09:04.490 --> 09:06.490
You... you're going back?

09:06.490 --> 09:07.330
Of course.

09:08.530 --> 09:11.010
I'm going to take back what's mine.

09:14.010 --> 09:16.490
There's no justice in this world.

09:18.010 --> 09:19.650
So I'll

09:20.300 --> 09:21.770
make my own.

09:22.250 --> 09:23.090
That time,

09:23.610 --> 09:25.250
he'd changed.

09:25.250 --> 09:26.100
He said

09:26.100 --> 09:27.250
he had a complicated identity.

09:27.490 --> 09:28.650
Once he reclaimed his birthright,

09:28.890 --> 09:30.220
he'd tell me everything.

09:31.980 --> 09:32.940
And then?

09:34.010 --> 09:35.820
We met one more time.

09:35.820 --> 09:36.770
When he came

09:38.580 --> 09:40.340
to talk to you about the engagement?

09:40.730 --> 09:41.570
Yes.

09:43.610 --> 09:44.450
That night,

09:44.770 --> 09:45.820
he talked and talked.

09:46.530 --> 09:49.610
For once, he seemed to have hope.

09:49.610 --> 09:50.490
But then he said

09:51.130 --> 09:52.890
he'd hurt Pingshu.

09:52.890 --> 09:54.820
He was terrified she wouldn't forgive him.

09:54.820 --> 09:56.370
He couldn't bring himself to tell her

09:56.370 --> 09:58.340
what he really was.

09:58.340 --> 10:00.420
He was afraid she'd leave him.

10:00.420 --> 10:02.300
His whole life was suffering.

10:03.850 --> 10:05.130
Bullied as a kid,

10:05.770 --> 10:07.250
he never learned to trust anyone.

10:07.650 --> 10:09.490
He finally met Ms. Cai, but even then,

10:10.530 --> 10:12.300
he couldn't give her his whole heart.

10:13.060 --> 10:14.100
In the end, that poor man

10:14.940 --> 10:16.250
died without even knowing why.

10:16.890 --> 10:17.730
No one

10:20.220 --> 10:21.420
even knows where his body is.

10:22.060 --> 10:23.060
I don't feel sorry for him at all.

10:25.580 --> 10:26.420
Young Master.

10:28.580 --> 10:30.180
Mu Zhengyang's hands were dripping with blood.

10:30.610 --> 10:31.770
He killed plenty who deserved it

10:31.770 --> 10:32.850
and plenty who didn't.

10:33.220 --> 10:34.980
He turned this whole martial world upside down,

10:35.730 --> 10:37.100
and my father got caught up in the wreckage.

10:38.100 --> 10:40.060
If he ended up in hell,

10:40.060 --> 10:40.980
good riddance.

10:41.250 --> 10:42.340
Young Master,

10:42.340 --> 10:44.610
I was just chatting with Miss Cai.

10:50.490 --> 10:51.340
Let me show you something.

11:00.650 --> 11:01.940
When did you plant this?

11:02.850 --> 11:04.130
After you and Song Yuzhi left.

11:05.060 --> 11:05.900
That long ago?

11:09.340 --> 11:10.180
Zhao,

11:12.100 --> 11:13.730
if you ever miss home,

11:13.730 --> 11:14.890
just come here and take a look.

11:27.130 --> 11:27.970
Mu Qingyan.

11:29.490 --> 11:30.940
I want to give you something too.

11:32.700 --> 11:33.540
Alright.

11:55.180 --> 11:57.300
Mu Qingyan's taken over the Bliss Palace.

11:58.010 --> 11:59.490
Why isn't Zhao back yet?

12:00.180 --> 12:02.180
Our dear junior sister, that traitor,

12:02.180 --> 12:03.650
finally got what she wanted.

12:03.650 --> 12:04.650
She's the wife of the Chief now.

12:05.060 --> 12:05.900
Why would she ever come back?

12:06.530 --> 12:07.370
Enough.

12:08.420 --> 12:09.260
Just stop.

12:10.010 --> 12:10.850
You are still defending her?

12:29.130 --> 12:29.970
Careful.

12:35.490 --> 12:36.420
Steps.

12:37.580 --> 12:38.420
Take my hand.

12:38.730 --> 12:39.570
First step.

12:40.180 --> 12:41.020
Second.

12:59.420 --> 13:00.260
There.

13:04.860 --> 13:06.100
(Peach Blossom Tavern)

13:06.100 --> 13:07.180
I promised you, remember?

13:07.490 --> 13:09.490
I'd share my childhood with you.

13:16.890 --> 13:17.730
Look.

13:18.100 --> 13:19.650
(Nutritious Pastry)
This is the pastry shop.

13:20.370 --> 13:21.300
Their peach blossom pastries

13:21.300 --> 13:22.300
are the best.

13:22.740 --> 13:23.650
(Ingenious Study)

13:23.650 --> 13:24.530
And next door

13:24.530 --> 13:26.060
is Ingenious Scholar's shop.

13:26.060 --> 13:28.530
There are so many storybooks there.

13:28.530 --> 13:29.730
There's this one mysterious little box,

13:30.490 --> 13:32.580
with books they'd never let kids touch.

13:36.220 --> 13:37.060
See this?

13:38.010 --> 13:39.180
We're catching ants.

13:43.940 --> 13:44.780
That's me?

13:46.650 --> 13:48.180
I said I'd share half with you,

13:48.530 --> 13:49.650
so you have to be here for it.

14:00.850 --> 14:01.940
The past

14:02.770 --> 14:03.650
is behind us.

14:04.530 --> 14:05.580
From now on,

14:06.370 --> 14:08.370
I just want you to be happy.

14:10.060 --> 14:11.700
You have a beautiful smile.

14:11.700 --> 14:12.650
You should use it more.

14:17.300 --> 14:19.610
And pay more attention to the people
around you.

14:20.340 --> 14:21.180
I believe

14:21.940 --> 14:23.300
that without those Sevens Pills,

14:24.340 --> 14:26.180
You Guanyue and the others still wouldn't
turn on you.

14:27.130 --> 14:28.300
You don't need to test people

14:28.940 --> 14:29.940
with life and death

14:30.530 --> 14:32.220
to earn real loyalty.

14:38.510 --> 14:39.370
Zhao.

14:39.370 --> 14:40.210
Mu Qingyan,

14:41.730 --> 14:42.570
I love you.

14:44.850 --> 14:45.820
I love you

14:47.130 --> 14:48.490
very much.

14:50.300 --> 14:51.580
No matter whether you

14:52.100 --> 14:52.940
deceived me,

14:54.100 --> 14:54.940
or even lost your mind,

14:57.890 --> 14:59.490
I can't stop myself

14:59.490 --> 15:00.490
from loving you.

15:02.890 --> 15:04.060
I love you so much

15:05.650 --> 15:08.220
that I once thought of giving you
everything I have.

15:09.370 --> 15:11.420
I want to know every part of you.

15:12.890 --> 15:14.370
I love you too much to lie to you.

15:15.650 --> 15:17.130
I love you enough that I can't watch you

15:17.890 --> 15:19.580
walk the same road as Mu Zhengyang.

15:21.220 --> 15:22.060
The truth is,

15:22.820 --> 15:25.060
even if I had known your plan
from the very beginning,

15:29.370 --> 15:30.820
I still would have chosen to save you.

15:32.940 --> 15:34.130
You're afraid

15:36.180 --> 15:37.100
of the dark.

15:38.700 --> 15:39.940
All that power,

15:41.180 --> 15:42.650
and you trust no one.

15:44.820 --> 15:46.580
If they crippled your cultivation,

15:48.650 --> 15:49.490
I can't imagine

15:52.580 --> 15:54.250
how you'd survive.

15:55.370 --> 15:56.610
But a path paved with corpses

15:58.100 --> 15:59.700
is not the way home.

16:03.890 --> 16:05.770
It'll just leave you with nothing.

16:07.220 --> 16:08.490
I don't want to be locked away.

16:10.940 --> 16:13.700
And I don't want you locked away either.

16:19.610 --> 16:20.450
Mu Qingyan,

16:24.100 --> 16:25.340
I have to go home.

16:35.530 --> 16:36.370
Zhao.

17:01.730 --> 17:02.570
Miss Cai!

17:02.980 --> 17:03.820
Miss Cai!

17:03.980 --> 17:05.250
We found a wedding dress shop!

17:13.730 --> 17:14.770
Miss Cai!

17:15.050 --> 17:15.890
Master You.

17:25.630 --> 17:26.490
Young Master.

17:26.490 --> 17:27.330
Where's Miss Cai?

17:29.250 --> 17:30.180
She left.

17:30.180 --> 17:31.020
She's gone?

17:31.730 --> 17:32.570
I'll bring her back.

17:32.570 --> 17:33.410
Don't.

17:35.730 --> 17:36.770
She won't come back.

17:56.380 --> 17:57.290
Yuzhi.

17:57.620 --> 17:59.180
You have the nerve to come back?!

17:59.180 --> 18:00.490
Father was good to you!

18:00.490 --> 18:01.940
And you shamelessly schemed with
that demon sect!

18:01.940 --> 18:03.810
You betrayed your master, your sect, for a man!

18:03.810 --> 18:04.650
You...

18:07.010 --> 18:08.290
What happens to Zhao

18:08.810 --> 18:10.290
should be decided by the lords.

18:12.660 --> 18:13.530
It's good you are back.

18:13.980 --> 18:14.820
It's good.

18:15.660 --> 18:17.130
Zhao, Master's waiting.

18:20.660 --> 18:21.500
Stop.

19:09.620 --> 19:11.500
(Righteous Spirit)

19:13.700 --> 19:14.770
My aunt's Sunshine Blade

19:15.570 --> 19:17.050
was meant for slaying demons.

19:17.810 --> 19:18.700
I'm not worthy to wield it.

19:29.490 --> 19:31.420
Grandfather forged this Heart-Protect Chain
for me,

19:31.980 --> 19:33.490
and I used it to save someone from
the demon sect.

19:34.250 --> 19:35.530
I'm not worthy of this either.

19:41.900 --> 19:43.330
Zhao. Zhao!

19:43.330 --> 19:44.170
No, no, don't.

19:45.220 --> 19:46.090
I, Cai Zhao, have betrayed

19:46.380 --> 19:47.220
my master and sect,

19:47.620 --> 19:48.660
colluded with the Demon Sect,

19:49.090 --> 19:50.010
maimed my fellow disciples, and

19:50.940 --> 19:51.810
shown disrespect to my elders.

19:52.940 --> 19:53.980
My crimes are unforgivable.

19:54.420 --> 19:55.660
Today, I sincerely plead guilty.

19:56.090 --> 19:57.140
Whatever punishment is decreed,

19:58.490 --> 19:59.330
I am willing

19:59.810 --> 20:00.810
to accept it without complaint.

20:02.420 --> 20:03.260
Cai Zhao,

20:04.250 --> 20:05.730
are you sure about this?

20:12.730 --> 20:14.090
Cai Zhao, traitorous disciple

20:14.700 --> 20:15.540
of Qingque Sect,

20:16.220 --> 20:17.900
receive your sentence. Accept your punishment.

20:20.570 --> 20:21.570
Betrayal of master and sect,

20:22.140 --> 20:23.010
alliance with the demon sect,

20:23.490 --> 20:24.730
defiance of all that is right,

20:25.140 --> 20:26.010
those are unforgivable crimes.

20:26.620 --> 20:27.460
It is only fitting

20:27.860 --> 20:28.940
that the sect be cleansed of her.

20:31.380 --> 20:32.860
I'd like to see

20:32.860 --> 20:34.180
who dares touch my daughter!

20:36.420 --> 20:37.420
Lord Cai.

20:37.420 --> 20:38.260
Please calm down.

20:38.860 --> 20:41.220
No one died because of what she did.

20:41.900 --> 20:43.490
Just strip her cultivation and be done with it.

20:44.330 --> 20:46.010
Strip her cultivation?

20:46.010 --> 20:48.490
What young person doesn't make mistakes?

20:48.490 --> 20:49.330
If you ask me,

20:49.330 --> 20:51.090
just let it go.

20:51.700 --> 20:53.490
Let Lord Cai take her home

20:53.490 --> 20:54.660
and deal with it privately.

20:55.700 --> 20:56.620
A household has its rules.

20:57.050 --> 20:58.220
A sect has its laws.

20:59.420 --> 21:01.940
If Cai Zhao walks away from this lightly,

21:02.330 --> 21:04.220
what's to stop other disciples

21:04.220 --> 21:05.220
from doing the same?

21:05.900 --> 21:06.940
Should we just

21:07.490 --> 21:08.570
let them off easy too?

21:09.660 --> 21:10.530
Li Wenxun,

21:10.530 --> 21:11.530
what do you want?

21:13.570 --> 21:16.380
Seven lashes from the Bone-Piercing
Python Whip.

21:16.940 --> 21:17.810
After that,

21:17.810 --> 21:19.490
confinement at the Thousandfold Cliff

21:19.810 --> 21:20.860
to reflect on her mistakes.

21:20.860 --> 21:21.700
No!

21:22.700 --> 21:23.730
Can anyone

21:23.730 --> 21:25.380
survive that Python Whip?

21:25.380 --> 21:26.490
Enough. Stop talking.

21:26.490 --> 21:27.330
Alright.

21:27.730 --> 21:28.570
Zhao.

21:29.220 --> 21:30.140
Mother.

21:30.140 --> 21:31.330
I made a grave mistake.

21:33.290 --> 21:34.130
I deserve this.

21:40.900 --> 21:42.180
After the punishment,

21:44.010 --> 21:45.290
no one speaks of this again.

21:45.940 --> 21:47.290
Mu Qingyan nearly killed my son.

21:47.290 --> 21:48.660
This is too lenient.

21:48.660 --> 21:49.500
You, Yang.

21:50.380 --> 21:52.090
If it weren't for Cai Pingshu back then,

21:52.090 --> 21:53.570
your entire family would've been

21:53.570 --> 21:55.770
turned into corpse slaves by Nie Hengcheng.

21:55.770 --> 21:57.490
Learn some mercy,

21:57.490 --> 21:58.810
you ungrateful mongrel.

21:59.180 --> 22:00.020
- Wenxun!
- You...

22:00.810 --> 22:01.650
Present the whip.

22:04.050 --> 22:05.050
As Sect Chief,

22:05.900 --> 22:07.140
I will carry this out myself.

23:58.940 --> 24:00.530
Execute!

25:15.570 --> 25:17.220
First lash!

25:52.010 --> 25:53.490
Second lash!

26:13.140 --> 26:14.660
Third lash!

26:29.420 --> 26:30.380
She's just a child.

26:30.380 --> 26:31.220
This is how you train her?

26:31.860 --> 26:33.290
When we became sworn brother and sister,

26:33.290 --> 26:35.010
I never pegged you for such a softie.

26:36.980 --> 26:37.860
Zhao.

26:37.860 --> 26:39.050
Let's go. No more training.

26:39.730 --> 26:40.570
I'll buy you candy.

26:43.180 --> 26:45.290
Candy! Candy!

26:45.290 --> 26:46.130
Yes.

26:46.140 --> 26:47.770
- Let's get candy!
- Candy!

26:47.770 --> 26:49.050
- Let's go!
- Buy candy.

26:49.380 --> 26:50.820
Candy!

26:50.820 --> 26:52.860
- Let's get candy!
- I love candy!

27:03.810 --> 27:06.250
Fourth lash!

27:52.090 --> 27:53.530
Fifth lash!

28:01.920 --> 28:02.770
- Don't!
- Zhao!

28:02.770 --> 28:03.610
You can't go.

28:03.610 --> 28:04.810
No, you can't.

28:29.330 --> 28:31.620
Sixth lash!

28:44.700 --> 28:46.980
I loved Yellow so much.

28:46.980 --> 28:48.980
Why did he bite me?

28:48.980 --> 28:52.180
I will never love a dog again.

28:57.980 --> 28:58.820
Zhao.

28:59.220 --> 29:00.380
Loving isn't wrong.

29:01.490 --> 29:03.490
If you find out you love the wrong thing,

29:03.980 --> 29:05.810
figure it out and set it right.

29:06.660 --> 29:08.660
There's so much beauty in this world.

29:09.290 --> 29:11.050
Don't let fear stop you

29:11.050 --> 29:12.140
from loving.

29:12.620 --> 29:13.460
Okay?

30:11.530 --> 30:13.250
Seventh lash!

30:20.570 --> 30:21.420
Zhao!

31:15.980 --> 31:16.860
Zhao!

32:53.220 --> 32:55.050
Qi Yunke didn't hold back at all.

32:56.010 --> 32:57.700
Zhao is just a girl,

32:57.700 --> 32:59.090
and he beat her so hard.

32:59.660 --> 33:01.140
And now she's locked away in the Realm Cavern

33:01.140 --> 33:02.330
for a whole year,

33:03.250 --> 33:04.490
no visits, no news.

33:05.700 --> 33:07.050
Stop pacing.

33:07.050 --> 33:08.530
We don't even know how she's doing.

33:09.290 --> 33:10.810
Just stop nagging.

33:12.810 --> 33:14.090
All the sect chiefs were there.

33:14.530 --> 33:16.730
Yunke is the head of the Six Sects.

33:17.620 --> 33:18.940
He already allowed Feicui

33:19.330 --> 33:20.770
to tend her wounds.

33:21.700 --> 33:22.980
Stop complaining.

33:22.980 --> 33:23.980
He already made an exception,

33:24.490 --> 33:25.620
letting Yuzhi look after her.

33:25.940 --> 33:26.780
I believe that Yuzhi

33:27.380 --> 33:28.490
will do everything he can

33:29.180 --> 33:30.090
to take care of Zhao.

33:30.490 --> 33:31.660
Then we'll have to

33:31.660 --> 33:32.810
rely on Yuzhi for that.

33:33.300 --> 33:35.020
(Righteous Spirit)

33:39.250 --> 33:40.090
I've prepared medicine.

33:40.570 --> 33:42.180
Zhao will recover once she takes it.

33:42.180 --> 33:43.020
No need.

33:43.730 --> 33:44.770
Those seven lashes

33:44.770 --> 33:46.050
damaged her meridians.

33:46.050 --> 33:47.250
No medicine can fix that.

33:47.250 --> 33:48.490
Enough.

33:48.490 --> 33:49.330
Xiaofeng.

33:49.490 --> 33:51.810
This is brewed from the Withered Branch.

33:52.940 --> 33:53.940
The Withered Branch?

34:00.010 --> 34:01.900
The one Pingshu planted?

34:03.290 --> 34:04.490
All these years,

34:04.490 --> 34:06.220
Lord Qi has been draining his inner power

34:06.220 --> 34:07.380
trying to heal Pingshu's injuries.

34:08.530 --> 34:10.610
He was waiting for this branch to bloom

34:10.610 --> 34:11.570
to use the flower as medicine.

34:11.570 --> 34:12.410
Enough said.

34:12.900 --> 34:15.490
This was always meant for Zhao.

34:16.380 --> 34:17.340
Take it to Yuzhi.

34:17.650 --> 34:18.820
Tell him to give it to her.

34:30.820 --> 34:36.300
(Realm Cavern)

35:09.530 --> 35:10.370
Zhao.

35:13.650 --> 35:14.490
Yuzhi.

35:16.170 --> 35:17.050
Drink this,

35:17.740 --> 35:18.580
and the pain will fade.

35:31.490 --> 35:32.570
Thank you, Yuzhi.

35:34.300 --> 35:35.140
Zhao,

35:36.090 --> 35:37.130
if it hurts, cry.

35:39.050 --> 35:39.890
I'm here.

35:40.260 --> 35:41.300
I'll stay with you.

35:44.900 --> 35:45.740
I'm fine.

35:48.820 --> 35:50.490
I just need some rest.

35:58.570 --> 36:00.610
Now that Nie Zhe is dead,

36:00.610 --> 36:03.090
Young Master, what are your plans?

36:03.650 --> 36:05.130
But the man in black behind him
is still out there.

36:06.570 --> 36:07.820
If we don't deal with him,

36:08.610 --> 36:10.090
he'll become a real threat.

36:10.200 --> 36:11.090
Young Master,

36:11.090 --> 36:11.930
this time

36:12.210 --> 36:14.980
Miss Cai took seven lashes from
the Python Whip.

36:15.940 --> 36:17.010
She'll live,

36:17.530 --> 36:18.690
but those wounds

36:19.050 --> 36:20.420
take time to heal.

36:21.260 --> 36:23.210
Lord Qi has confined he

36:23.210 --> 36:26.940
to the Realm Cavern at the Thousandfold Cliff

36:27.490 --> 36:28.740
for a year of solitary reflection.

36:30.610 --> 36:31.650
In this future year,

36:32.570 --> 36:33.820
only Song Yuzhi

36:34.170 --> 36:35.300
is allowed in or out

36:35.610 --> 36:36.450
to tend to her.

36:36.980 --> 36:38.490
From now on, she is her,

36:38.490 --> 36:39.330
and I am me.

36:39.980 --> 36:41.740
From now on, throughout the Li Sect,

36:41.740 --> 36:44.010
no one speaks of her again.

36:47.400 --> 36:58.060
=Generation to Generation=

37:16.820 --> 37:21.230
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

37:21.795 --> 37:26.410
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

37:26.750 --> 37:31.315
♪With a shining cup,
I drink with delight tonight♪

37:31.840 --> 37:36.140
♪Free to wander in the world♪

37:39.085 --> 37:43.785
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

37:44.310 --> 37:48.600
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

37:49.260 --> 37:53.290
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

37:53.605 --> 37:58.730
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

37:59.305 --> 38:04.115
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

38:04.330 --> 38:08.500
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

38:09.225 --> 38:13.160
♪I freely roam in the world♪

38:13.660 --> 38:18.935
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪

38:41.665 --> 38:46.795
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

38:47.160 --> 38:51.530
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

38:51.795 --> 38:55.925
♪I freely roam in the world♪

38:56.110 --> 39:01.685
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪
